'''''Shangani Patrol''''' ni filime y'intambara ishingiye ku gitabo kitari ibihimbano ''A Time to Die'' cyanditswe na Robert Cary (1968)<ref>The Shangani Patrol (rhodesia.nl)</ref>, hamwe n’amateka ya Shangani Patrol, hamwe na Brian O'Shaughnessy nka Major Allan Wilson na Will Hutchins nk'umuskuti Frederick. Russell Burnham . <ref>Shangani Patrol soundtrack album cover, RPM 1053-S, RPM Film Studios, South Africa, 1970.</ref> Harimo n'indirimbo "Shangani Patrol" ya Nick Taylor (recording 1966).<ref>Shangani Patrol Memorial POI | Trailforks <nowiki>https://www.trailforks.com</nowiki> › ... › Matopos</ref>

Ku buyobozi bwa Major Wilson, irondo rikurikirana umwami Ndebele Lobengula wahunze hakurya y'uruzi rwa Shangani<ref>Major Allan Wilson and the Shangani Patrol 1893 - David Snape <nowiki>https://www.foyles.co.uk</nowiki> › witem › biography › the-fir...</ref>. Bagabanijwe ku mbaraga nyamukuru, batewe igico na Ndebele impi kandi<ref>Shangani Patrol (1970) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › shangani-patrol</ref>, usibye abagabo bake boherejwe nk'imbaraga, bose baricwa<ref>Shangani Patrol (1970) — The Movie Database (TMDB) (themoviedb.org)</ref>. Ubwo ni bwo butwari bw'irondo rya Shangani ku buryo Ndebele watsinze yagize ati: "Bari abagabo ariko na ba se bari abagabo mbere yabo<ref>Shangani Patrol (1970) - Badmovies.org <nowiki>https://www.badmovies.org</nowiki> › forum</ref>." Ukurikije uko umuntu abibona, ibyabaye byari rimwe mu makosa akomeye no kwibeshya kwa gisirikare muri iki gihe cy'amateka, cyangwa igihagararo cyanyuma cyintwari cya bake<ref>The Shangani Patrol - Historical Novel Society <nowiki>https://historicalnovelsociety.org</nowiki> › Reviews</ref>. Ibyabaye byari bifite akamaro gakomeye mubwongereza, Afrika yepfo, na Rodeziya bihwanye na ' Custer's Last stand '. Ngiyo inkuru yabo, yavuzwe muri firime ya 1970 yafatiwe ahitwa Matabeleland, Rhodesia (ubu ni muri [[Zimbabwe]]).<ref>Three oral history statements made in 1937 by amaNdebele ... <nowiki>https://zimfieldguide.com</nowiki> › matabeleland-north › three-...</ref>
